a=fyb_news&rsv_dl=fyb_news"},{"index":24,"title":"女子在酒吧被陌生人投放“伟哥”","desc":"安徽滁州程女士在清吧遭陌生男子韩某搭讪并向其酒杯投放100mg西地那非（伟哥）。监控显示韩某趁其如厕时下药，程女士发现杯中异物后报警。警方初以无犯罪事实为由调解，韩某赔偿1.3万元，后程女士撤销协议并启动法律程序。","pic":"https:\/\/fyb-2.cdn.bcebos.com\/hotboard_image\/d4cf6ef3f3e5a650e540ae80b4fd5968","url":"https:\/\/www.baidu.com\/s?wd=%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E5%9C%A8%E9%85%92%E5%90%A7%E8%A2%AB%E9%99%8C%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%BA%E6%8A%95%E6%94%BE%E2%80%9C%E4%BC%9F%E5%93%A5%E2%80%9D&sa=fyb_news&rsv_dl=fyb_news","hot":"5710103","mobilUrl":"https:\/\/www.baidu.com\/s?wd=%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E5%9C%A8%E9%85%92%E5%90%A7%E8%A2%AB%E9%99%8C%E7%94%9F%E4%BA%BA%E6%8A%95%E6%94%BE%E2%80%9C%E4%BC%9F%E5%93%A5%E2%80%9D&sa=fyb_news&rsv_dl=fyb_news"},{"index":25,"title":"俄乌双方伤亡近180万人","desc":"当地时间6月28日，历经1580余天的拉锯，俄乌冲突的持续时长已超过第一次世界大战。双方累计伤亡人数接近180万，是二战后国家间冲突中最为惨烈的一次。","pic":"https:\/\/fyb-2.cdn.bcebos.com\/hotboard_image\/6bb80bdbf86dbd0138caf2857e510505","url":"https:\/\/www.baidu.com\/s?wd=%E4%BF%84%E4%B9%8C%E5%8F%8C%E6%96%B9%E4%BC%A4%E4%BA%A1%E8%BF%91180%E4%B8%87%E4%BA%BA&sa=fyb_news&rsv_dl=fyb_news","hot":"5616001","mobilUrl":"https:\/\/www.baidu.com\/s?wd=%E4%BF%84%E4%B9%8C%E5%8F%8C%E6%96%B9%E4%BC%A4%E4%BA%A1%E8%BF%91180%E4%B8%87%E4%BA%BA&sa=fyb_news&rsv_dl=fyb_news"},{"index":26,"title":"法媒点赞中国小区楼顶“人工降雨”","desc":"6月27日，法国24小时电视台在社交媒体分享中国山西某小区楼顶人工降雨系统的降温方案，称其在40℃高温下通过蒸发吸热有效缓解炎热。该报道引发关注之际，法国正遭遇持续高温天气。","pic":"https:\/\/fyb-2.cdn.bcebos.com\/hotboard_image\/7318fe67c4b1c5e310a1edd73dd2f17c","url":"https:\/\/www.baidu.com\/s?wd=%E6%B3%95%E5%AA%92%E7%82%B9%E8%B5%9E%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%B0%8F%E5%8C%BA%E6%A5%BC%E9%A1%B6%E2%80%9C%E4%BA%BA%E5%B7%A5%E9%99%8D%E9%9B%A8%E2%80%9D&sa=fyb_news&rsv_dl=fyb_news","hot":"5513003","mobilUrl":"https:\/\/www.baidu.com\/s?wd=%E6%B3%95%E5%AA%92%E7%82%B9%E8%B5%9E%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E5%B0%8F%E5%8C%BA%E6%A5%BC%E9%A1%B6%E2%80%9C%E4%BA%BA%E5%B7%A5%E9%99%8D%E9%9B%A8%E2%80%9D&sa=fyb_news&rsv_dl=fyb_news"},{"index":27,"title":"日本世界杯淘汰赛历史0胜","desc":"日本男足自1998年首次晋级世界杯决赛圈以来，共四次闯入淘汰赛阶段，但均未能取得胜利，巴西若输日本将创36年最差